data.description:
You must see this gorgeous spacious home. 4 Bedroom 2 bath 2 car attached garage. It can be 3 bedrooms with an office. Nice drive up appeal with nice landscaping. Mud room from garage into the house and a full size laundry room. Covered sunroom on back of the home to relax in the shade on sunny days. Floors are beautiful engineered hardwood. Kitchen features lots of cabinets with lots of storage and a walk in pantry, Large Kitchen Island, granite counter tops, beautiful backsplash. Large Dining room overlooking large living area.  Large Master Bedroom with master bath with shower. 
Dual sinks vanity with granite countertops and features a large walk in closet. Sprinkler system and gutters. Lots of Amenities in Heartland. Check out all the amenities at heartlandtexas.com. Too many to list. The Sellers Disclosure is in the transaction desk.  Please print and submit the signed sellers Disclosure with all offers. Buyers will need too purchase a survey. Show to your pickiest buyers.
